---
import "../../styles/theme.css";
import "../../styles/landing.css";

const _canonicalURL = "https://freellms.vercel.app/alternatives/openrouter/";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="canonical" href={canonicalURL} />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Geist+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>FreeLLM vs OpenRouter: Self-hosted, no credits required</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="FreeLLM is a self-hosted alternative to OpenRouter. Your API keys and prompts stay on your own infrastructure. Zero per-request cost."
    />
    <meta property="og:title" content="FreeLLM vs OpenRouter: Self-hosted, no credits required" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="FreeLLM is a self-hosted alternative to OpenRouter. Your API keys and prompts stay on your own infrastructure. Zero per-request cost."
    />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/og-image.png" />
    <meta property="og:url" content={canonicalURL} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="/og-image.png" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <LandingHeader />
    <main>
      <article class="alt-page">
        <span class="page-eyebrow">comparison</span>
        <h1>FreeLLM vs OpenRouter</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Both aggregate multiple LLM providers behind one OpenAI-compatible API. The key difference
          is where your keys and data live. OpenRouter is a managed cloud service that proxies your
          requests through their infrastructure. FreeLLM runs on your own infra, so your prompts and
          API keys never leave your servers.
        </p>

        <h2>Side-by-side comparison</h2>

        <div class="table-shell">
          <table class="alt-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Feature</th>
                <th class="freellm-col">FreeLLM</th>
                <th>OpenRouter</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Cost model</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Free-tier only, zero markup</td>
                <td>Per-token pricing with markup on paid models</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Hosting</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Self-hosted on your infra</td>
                <td>Managed cloud (their servers)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Data stays on your infra</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Yes</td>
                <td class="no">No</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Setup time</td>
                <td class="freellm-col">~2 min (Railway or Render deploy)</td>
                <td>Instant (sign up and go)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Number of providers</td>
                <td class="freellm-col">8 free-tier providers</td>
                <td>100+ providers (paid and free)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>OpenAI SDK compatible</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Yes</td>
                <td class="yes">Yes</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Dashboard</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Real-time, included</td>
                <td class="yes">Yes (cloud dashboard)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Automatic failover</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Yes</td>
                <td class="yes">Yes</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2>When to use OpenRouter instead</h2>
        <p>
          OpenRouter is the better choice in these situations:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>You need paid models like GPT-4o, Claude 3.5 Sonnet, or Gemini Ultra. FreeLLM only covers free tiers.</li>
          <li>You do not want to manage infrastructure. OpenRouter is fully managed and requires no deploy step.</li>
          <li>You need access to providers beyond the 8 free-tier ones FreeLLM ships with.</li>
          <li>You are fine with your prompts transiting OpenRouter's servers.</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="divider" />

        <h2>When FreeLLM makes sense</h2>
        <p>
          FreeLLM fits better when any of these apply:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>You want your prompts and API keys to stay on servers you control. Useful when working with sensitive data or internal tooling.</li>
          <li>You need zero recurring cost. No credits, no per-token markup, no surprise bills.</li>
          <li>You are building something where data residency matters, such as internal enterprise tools or regulated industries.</li>
          <li>You want circuit breakers, response caching (~23ms cache hits), and virtual sub-keys without building them yourself.</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="divider" />

        <h2>The code change is two lines</h2>
        <p>
          If you are already on OpenRouter, switching to FreeLLM is a base URL and key swap. The rest of
          your code stays the same.
        </p>

        <div class="code-shell">
          <div class="code-label">python — before (OpenRouter)</div>
          <pre><code><span class="token-keyword">from</span> <span class="token-var">openai</span> <span class="token-keyword">import</span> <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span>

<span class="token-var">client</span> = <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span>(
    <span class="token-var">base_url</span>=<span class="token-string">"https://openrouter.ai/api/v1"</span>,
    <span class="token-var">api_key</span>=<span class="token-string">"sk-or-..."</span>
)</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="code-shell">
          <div class="code-label">python — after (FreeLLM)</div>
          <pre><code><span class="token-keyword">from</span> <span class="token-var">openai</span> <span class="token-keyword">import</span> <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span>

<span class="token-var">client</span> = <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span>(
    <span class="token-var">base_url</span>=<span class="token-string">"https://your-freellm-instance/v1"</span>,  <span class="token-comment"># your own server</span>
    <span class="token-var">api_key</span>=<span class="token-string">"your-freellm-key"</span>
)</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-block">
          <p>Deploy FreeLLM to Railway or Render in about 2 minutes. Your keys stay on your server.</p>
          <a href="/quickstart/" class="btn-primary">Deploy FreeLLM in 2 minutes</a>
          <div class="cta-links">
            <a href="https://github.com/Devansh-365/freellm" class="btn-ghost">Star on GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </main>
    <LandingFooter />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .alt-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 8rem;
  }

  .alt-page .page-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.875rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.18);
    color: hsl(158, 50%, 65%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .alt-page h1 {
    font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .alt-page .lead {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 65%);
    margin: 0 0 3.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  .alt-page h2 {
    font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 3rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .alt-page p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 65%);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .alt-page ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .alt-page ul li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 65%);
  }

  .table-shell {
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 22%);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .alt-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    background: hsl(224, 14%, 15%);
  }

  .alt-table th {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    text-align: left;
    background: hsl(224, 14%, 13%);
    color: hsl(158, 50%, 65%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 22%);
  }

  .alt-table td {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.07);
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 75%);
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  .alt-table tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .alt-table tbody tr:hover { background: hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.03); }
  .alt-table td:first-child { color: hsl(0, 0%, 85%); font-weight: 500; }
  .alt-table .freellm-col { background: hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.05); }

  .yes { color: hsl(158, 50%, 60%); font-weight: 600; font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace; }
  .no { color: hsl(0, 50%, 55%); font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace; }
  .partial { color: hsl(38, 90%, 55%); font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace; }

  .code-shell {
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 22%);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .code-label {
    padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
    background: hsl(224, 14%, 13%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 22%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 50%);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .code-shell pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    background: hsl(224, 14%, 15%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 88%);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .code-shell code { background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; color: inherit; font-size: inherit; }
  .token-comment { color: hsl(0, 0%, 45%); }
  .token-keyword { color: hsl(200, 80%, 65%); }
  .token-string  { color: hsl(158, 50%, 60%); }
  .token-var     { color: hsl(0, 0%, 85%); }

  .cta-block {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.2);
    background: hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.04);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-block p { color: hsl(0, 0%, 65%); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .cta-block .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: hsl(158, 50%, 46%);
    color: #04140a;
    font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 280ms cubic-bezier(0.32, 0.72, 0, 1);
  }

  .cta-block .btn-primary:hover { background: hsl(158, 50%, 50%); transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .cta-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-links .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.375rem;
    padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: transparent;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 65%);
    font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 28%);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 280ms cubic-bezier(0.32, 0.72, 0, 1);
  }

  .cta-links .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: hsl(224, 12%, 40%); color: hsl(0, 0%, 85%); }

  .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 20%); margin: 3rem 0; }
</style>
